OL,3,CStaff member at NHS trust that failed
OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,FReport by Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,7,FBarry and Health Producer Helena
OL,8,FLambert
OL,10,FA member of staff, who worked at the
OL,11,FNHS mental health trust that treated
OL,12,FValdo Calocane, has told ITV News
OL,13,Fthere will be "another disaster" in
OL,14,Fthe organisation.
OL,16,FThe NHS worker says she was silenced
OL,17,Fwhen she tried to blow the whistle
OL,18,Fover safety concerns at the trust -
OL,19,Fthe stress even led her to contemplate
OL,20,Fsuicide.
