OL,3,CStaff member at NHS trust that failed
OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,FIt comes as an independent report
OL,7,Frevealed a series of failures by
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust during the care and
OL,10,Ftreatment of Calocane, before he
OL,11,Fkilled three people.
OL,13,FCalocane, who was diagnosed with
OL,14,Fparanoid schizophrenia, killed Barnaby
OL,15,FWebber, Grace O'Malley-Kumar and Ian
OL,16,FCoates in Nottingham in June 2023.
OL,18,FThe victims' families are calling for
OL,19,Fa full statutory inquiry to examine
OL,20,Ftheir deaths and "wider failings" in
OL,21,Fmental health services.
