OL,6,FThe independent review found:
OL,8,FITV News has spoken to a staff member
OL,9,Fwho worked at Nottinghamshire
OL,10,FHealthcare NHS foundation Trust during
OL,11,FCalocane's treatment, though she
OL,12,Fwasn't involved in his care.
OL,14,FThe mental health worker, who has
OL,15,Fasked to remain anonymous, claims when
OL,16,Fshe tried to raise other safety
OL,17,Fconcerns at the trust she was targeted
OL,18,Fby her bosses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
