OL,3,CStaff member at NHS trust that failed
OL,4,Cto stop triple killer speaks out
OL,6,F"I was ostracised and victimised by
OL,7,Fthe organisation and I felt
OL,8,Fpowerless", she told ITV News.
OL,10,F"I felt pushed to the brink - and even
OL,11,Fconsidered taking my own life."
OL,13,FShe echoes the report's findings about
OL,14,Fover-stretched staff.
OL,16,F"Cost-cutting is down to the bone. We
OL,17,Fjust couldn't keep staff because of
OL,18,Fthe working conditions.
