OL,6,F"People don't go to work to make
OL,7,Fmistakes. It's the system that has
OL,8,Fallowed the failures."
OL,10,FThe whistleblower told ITV News that
OL,11,Flessons have not been learnt and she
OL,12,Ffears there could be a further tragedy
OL,13,Fat the trust.
OL,15,F"If staff don't feel confident to
OL,16,Fspeak up, it will definitely happen
OL,17,Fagain. There will be another disaster
OL,18,Fat the trust."
