OL,6,F"We are making clear progress with a
OL,7,FTrust-wide plan, which is already
OL,8,Fdelivering key improvements in areas
OL,9,Fsuch as risk assessment and discharge
OL,10,Fprocesses. We are also improving the
OL,11,Fway we listen and engage with
OL,12,Fpatients, families, our colleagues,
OL,13,Fand local partners - to make sure
OL,14,Fconcerns are acted on as quickly as
